Play around with the co-variates used in [LASSO Regression](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lasso_(statistics)) and see the results updated below.  The underlying analsyis is performed using the [R](https://www.r-project.org/) package [glmnet](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/glmnet/) and it is recommended you read the packages [vignette](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/glmnet/vignettes/glmnet\_beta.html), in particular the section on logistic regression.
